#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:2 a14c5b0260124682869eea973e99627f
msgid "Earlier Releases"
msgstr "早期版本"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:4 082e081a5e624bc5aec929dde9b2cbde
msgid ""
"This page summarizes the earlier VoxCPM releases that remain useful for "
"compatibility, lighter deployment targets, and historical reference. For "
"new projects, use :doc:`./voxcpm2`."
msgstr ""
"本页概述仍有价值的早期 VoxCPM 版本，适用于兼容、更轻部署目标与历史参照。"
"新项目请使用 :doc:`./voxcpm2`。"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:7 9430285412cb48008fec6125549a7188
