msgstr "何时选用早期版本"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:9 c62c8043af594eccb47cdacaf10ac1b0
msgid "Choose an earlier release if you need one of the following:"
msgstr "若你需要以下任一情况，可选用早期版本："

