#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:37 8ec7f530d96144e9b808f0edc627c4af
msgid "VoxCPM 1.5"
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.5"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:39 a863dee15a344d44b3f5fa9edd7e3b20
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 1.5 is the final 1.x upgrade before VoxCPM 2. It improves audio "
"quality and efficiency while keeping the core context-aware generation "
"and zero-shot voice cloning workflow familiar to existing 1.x users."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 1.5 是 VoxCPM 2 之前 1.x 的最后一次升级。它在提升音质与效率的同时，"
"保留原有 1.x 用户熟悉的上下文感知生成与零样本声音克隆流程。"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:41 ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:55
#: 1cd84c88da6540feaed42e4080b412e1 7a7c5433e4f8475da0cdbf4144fab832
msgid "Key characteristics:"
msgstr "主要特点："

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:43 9df247bbf82b48db91abf0f912ac3628
msgid "44.1kHz output"
msgstr "44.1kHz 输出"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:44 db3baaf59f3a4f228968cabd8877ac9b
msgid "6.25Hz LM token rate"
msgstr "6.25Hz 的 LM token 速率"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:45 b4c52d132bcd410f945d4967468ec1cb
msgid "patch size increased from 2 to 4"
msgstr "patch 大小由 2 增至 4"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:46 8343ec9b37f9447d8ca65a10533c014f
msgid "simpler migration path for existing VoxCPM 1.0 users"
msgstr "对既有 VoxCPM 1.0 用户迁移路径更简单"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:48 f20b68725f6247749c4e7575822632b6
msgid ""
"Use VoxCPM 1.5 when you want a lighter Chinese/English checkpoint than "
"VoxCPM 2, while keeping stronger output quality than VoxCPM 1.0."
msgstr ""
"若你需要比 VoxCPM 2 更轻的中英 checkpoint，同时又要比 VoxCPM 1.0 更高的输出质量，可选用 VoxCPM 1.5。"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:51 10effc0cc5384f368745678da1564c40
msgid "VoxCPM 1.0"
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.0"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:53 7a4f637634bd4f2d81099b3cd532704f
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 1.0 is the original tokenizer-free VoxCPM release. It remains "
"useful as the baseline reference point for the family and for older "
"experiments built around the original 0.5B checkpoint."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 1.0 是初代无分词器 VoxCPM 发布版，仍是全系列的基线参照，也适用于围绕原始 0.5B checkpoint 的早期实验。"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:57 de018ec8e5234183a0557db8901c6f98
msgid "600M parameter size"
msgstr "600M 参数量"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:58 10f4225ee65742ac971b88cce7f7cc40
msgid "16kHz output"
msgstr "16kHz 输出"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:59 24c0672fd08f44859e18756f6edc87b4
msgid "original VoxCPM architecture release"
msgstr "原始 VoxCPM 架构发布"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:60 7cc2b3ffa23441519ffc1d8ab87af78f
msgid "benchmark reference for early VoxCPM results"
msgstr "早期 VoxCPM 结果的基准参照"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:62 9df4b82d6c51406cb7005aa63ff8a581
msgid ""
"Use VoxCPM 1.0 when you need the smallest historical checkpoint or want "
"to compare against the original baseline behavior."
msgstr ""
"若你需要体积最小的历史 checkpoint，或要与原始基线行为对比，可使用 VoxCPM 1.0。"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:65 f703af5daa224d06b8a4c020c174d60d
msgid "Migration Guidance"
msgstr "迁移建议"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:67 aaa2ac90ad394ef59e3014b2cc7f9e75
msgid "New projects should start with :doc:`./voxcpm2`."
msgstr "新项目请从 :doc:`./voxcpm2` 开始。"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:68 c3a76ec0462a420baa5b80a8f17a4895
msgid ""
"Existing VoxCPM 1.0 users should generally move to VoxCPM 1.5 first if "
"they need a lower-risk 1.x upgrade path."
msgstr ""
"既有 VoxCPM 1.0 用户若希望走风险更低的 1.x 升级路径，一般应先迁到 VoxCPM 1.5。"

#: ../../models/earlier_releases.rst:69 2c569d1d13ba4265b8cf130de350fc34
msgid ""
"If you need multilingual synthesis, Voice Design, Style Control, or 48kHz"
" output, move directly to :doc:`./voxcpm2`."
msgstr ""
"若你需要多语种合成、Voice Design、Style Control 或 48kHz 输出，请直接升级到 :doc:`./voxcpm2`。"

